ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.message

Class PMU_B07

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.message.PMU_B07
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class PMU_B07
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a PMU_B07 message structure (see chapter 15.3.8). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message Header)
    • 2: SFT (Software Segment) optional repeating
    • 3: UAC (User Authentication Credential Segment) optional
    • 4: EVN (Event Type)
    • 5: STF (Staff Identification)
    • 6: PRA (Practitioner Detail) optional
    • 7: PMU_B07_CERTIFICATE (a Group object) optional repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
